      <section id="section-case" class="site-section">
        <h3 class="hca-text--title">Case</h3>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-5">
            <div class="site-container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-text--body-1">Much like font weight, case should only be used to add obvious context or hierarchy.</p>
              <p class="hca-text--body-1">Avoid using all caps unless needed to clearly establish a contextual hierarchy, or unless your intention is to SHOUT AT YOUR USER.</p>
              <p class="hca-text--body-1">There are very few situations in which you should need to use all caps text.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-7">
            <div class="row">
